/faces/normal/devil.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />#fatc"},{"pid":"c89103a2ffa31d4d2345a169b30efcb5339787aa","tid":937719,"uid":139573,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:15:04.000Z","msg":"樓主想講飛矢不動<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder2.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n　　芝諾問他的學生：&ldquo;一支射出的箭是動的還是不動的？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;那還用說，當然是動的。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;確實是這樣，在每個人的眼裡它都是動的。可是，這支箭在每一個瞬間里都有它的位置嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;有的，老師。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;在這一瞬間里，它占據的空間和它的體積一樣嗎？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;有確定的位置，又占據著和自身體積一樣大小的空間。&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;那麼，在這一瞬間里，這支箭是動的，還是不動的？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;不動的，老師&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;這一瞬間是不動的，那麼其他瞬間呢？&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;也是不動的，老師&rdquo;<br />\n<br />\n　　&ldquo;所以，射出去的箭是不動的？&rdquo;"},{"pid":"c77e51743aa311f9054740af418939e180156911","tid":937719,"uid":157439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"Planck time?"},{"pid":"2c5688cc5de0eeba52d125e284f351d992b27709","tid":937719,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"c77e51743aa311f9054740af418939e180156911","tid":937719,"uid":157439,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:37:32.000Z","msg":"Planck time?"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T04:57:45.000Z","msg":"睇睇先<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f7eb6c658a0886437009b2b712982be1d4bf104f","tid":937719,"uid":141869,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2018-12-12T05:01:11.000Z","msg":"其實時間係人定義出來，同長度一樣，<br />\n可以無限分割，<br />\n<br />\n真正無法無限分割嘅係佢地對應測量嘅物品，<br />\n長度對應物體大小，去到原子 夸克級別，<br />\n<br />\n時間對應嘅，我覺得係<br />\n品物產生變化所需的最短時間<br />\n<br />\n有啲1999，有冇人明我講咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98db9c2e1d56d02b05dcd7a508e2e7155d1390e3","tid":937719,"uid":213441,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"f7eb6c658a0886437009b2b712982be1d4bf